cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with generating images from text, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of a deep learning architecture (StackGAN-v2) suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the use of a large dataset (recipe1M) and the need to understand the textual structure of recipes suggests that the paper may also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR).
